{
  "texts": [
    "o Explore methods for integrating LLMs into blended learning environments, ensuring they complement humanled instruction without compromising pedagogical standards.",
    "o Investigate effective training programs for educators, enabling them to leverage LLMs to enhance teaching quality and student engagement.• Bias Detection and Mitigation o Design and implement bias-detection algorithms to monitor and reduce biases in LLM outputs, particularly in diverse educational contexts.",
    "o Explore techniques for creating fair and diverse training datasets to minimize systemic biases and ensure equity across student groups.",
    "o Study the impact of bias on educational outcomes and develop strategies to address unintended consequences in LLM-driven applications.• Privacy and Security Enhancements Review Discover Sustainability (2025) 6:27 | https://doi.org/10.1007/s43621-025-00815-8 o Investigate advanced data encryption techniques and anonymization protocols to safeguard sensitive student information during LLM deployment.",
    "o Develop privacy-preserving frameworks that comply with evolving data protection regulations (e.g., GDPR, FERPA)."
  ]
}